title: Ep. - 300 - ASHLEY DARBY FROM REAL HOUSEWIVES OF POTOMAC THE BACHELORETTE REVIEW
description:
Ashley Darby from Real Housewives of Potomac talks about life before Bravo, her marriage to Michael, her new pregnancy, and this season of the Bravo show.

 

Another Bachelor Podcast co-hosts Dylan, Nick, and Patrick help Kate review this season of The Bachelorette.
